{"seq": 10, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-23T17:34:52+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:liu_zhengfeng:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3496, "out": 263, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "大清早費彬就來了，嵩山派果然盯得緊。客氣話得先說，免得落人口實，只要平安過了今日，一切都好說。", "action": {"kind": "speak", "target_area": "", "target_agent": "費彬", "utterance": "費師兄早，嵩山派遠道而來，劉某未曾遠迎，還請見諒。廳內已備好茶水，師兄請入內稍作歇息。", "object": ""}, "plan": "先禮貌招待嵩山派的人，穩住場面，確保洗手大典順利進行。"}, "error": null}}
{"seq": 11, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-23T17:34:54+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:linghu_chong:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3400, "out": 121, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "一大早的，劉府那邊估計已經熱鬧起來了，先去街上逛逛，看看能不能找壇好酒暖暖身子。", "action": {"kind": "move_to", "target_area": "市集", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": ""}, "plan": "先去市集看看有沒有什麼好酒，然後再晃去劉府湊湊熱鬧。"}, "error": null}}
{"seq": 12, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-23T17:34:54+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:yi_lin:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3385, "out": 192, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "這裡冷清清的，一個人待著真怕。師父她們應該都去劉府賀禮了吧，我得趕快去跟師父會合才行。", "action": {"kind": "move_to", "target_area": "演武場", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": ""}, "plan": "前往熱鬧的演武場，看看能不能在那裡找到師父定逸師太。"}, "error": null}}
{"seq": 13, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-23T17:34:54+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:tian_boguang:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3479, "out": 200, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "曲洋那老頭在城外待著，正好，省得被他瞧見。我得去城裡轉轉，把那小尼姑找出來才是正經事。", "action": {"kind": "move_to", "target_area": "長街", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": ""}, "plan": "先到長街或是人多的地方逛逛，看看能不能碰上昨天那個落單的小尼姑。"}, "error": null}}
{"seq": 14, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-23T17:34:54+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:fei_bin:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3479, "out": 255, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "劉正風這老傢伙還想退出江湖？盟主交代的差事絕不能在他手裡黃了，我得進去廳堂，時刻盯著他。", "action": {"kind": "move_to", "target_area": "劉府", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": ""}, "plan": "先進入劉府廳堂，占個好位置，伺機向劉正風施壓，確保他洗手大典辦不成。"}, "error": null}}
{"seq": 15, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-23T17:34:54+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:qu_yang:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3481, "out": 295, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "田伯光這傢伙怎麼會在群玉院？若他在城內搗亂，只怕會壞了正風的好事。我得遠遠避著，決不能讓這渾人發現我的蹤跡，更不能讓正道盯上我。", "action": {"kind": "wait", "target_area": "", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": "在荒祠的角落裡觀察城內動靜，保持隱蔽。"}, "plan": "暫時留在城外，觀察城門方向的動靜，避開人群進入衡山城。"}, "error": null}}
