{"seq": 156, "tick": 7, "wall": "2026-07-23T17:36:12+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "7:tian_boguang:reply", "tier": "dialogue", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 4164, "out": 138, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "這小子倒是上鉤得快，這下就能把他支開，儀琳那邊就沒人護著了。先把令狐沖灌醉或者拖住，正事要緊。", "action": {"kind": "move_to", "target_area": "迴雁樓", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": ""}, "plan": "帶令狐沖去迴雁樓，趁著他喝酒時找機會甩開他或是讓他醉死，回頭去找儀琳。"}, "error": null}}
